I"V<p><strong>Large fiend (devil), lawful evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 19 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 300 (24d10+168)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft., fly 60 ft.</p>

